{"type": "article", "id": 49468, "title": "肯德基重现小虎队和 TFboys 隔空对唱，OPPO 新年广告不错 | 乙方日报", "description": "这里有营销和营销人相关的一切", "date": "2018-01-22T04:13:49Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 47240, "name": "TFboys"}, {"id": 3688, "name": "OPPO"}], "category": 18, "column": 31, "author": 26306, "comment_count": 32, "praise_count": 93, "image": "img/article/article_show/20180122120231TACFj2O1qrYNe8K9.jpg", "contents": "<h3 nocleanhtml=\"true\">明星又代言了啥</h3><p class=\"\"><a href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MjM5MzYxMjI0NQ==&amp;mid=2659126971&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=dc88b8a6166021f36fa322147ba0a742&amp;chksm=bd1fc6018a684f17bdcf8b919d90ac51daf2ae449fa9907fe1dbc521b4c14cbd2b7ef68a60cc&amp;scene=0&amp;key=fba83162a4a8645b30917cf3f8e68ae813168e319f39ed99656cbfdb732a9dd8bfae9741a9566c39ed1a1c77d2e3066e9a27e39147edc274cf197d49c84a818f5fb6fb29888d70578be1a4b92f7b17e0&amp;ascene=0&amp;uin=MTIyNTYzODY0MA%3D%3D&amp;devicetype=iMac+MacBookAir6%2C2+OSX+OSX+10.10.5+build(14F2511)&amp;version=11000006&amp;lang=zh_CN&amp;pass_ticket=SN8n2E2s%2BxXG9uJ84UlFnB6VXIZK2qW%2F1rDq3fTalSGbq7KIADhWKMjgkHm73zFt\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>肯德基新年营销，重现小虎队和 TFboys 隔空对唱</b></a>，以 2018 年和小虎队出道的 1988 年对比三十年来人们的生活变迁，同时上架了 KFC 新春桶。</p><div class=\"com-insert-embed com-insert-embeds\">\r\n\t<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n\t\t<iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"https://v.qq.com/iframe/player.html?vid=v0025t8mhzw&amp;tiny=0&amp;auto=0\" allowfullscreen=\"\"></iframe>\r\n\t</figure>\r\n\t\r\n</div><p>        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 14.0px 'Heiti SC Light'; color: #323333; -webkit-text-stroke: #323333} p.p2 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 14.0px 'Heiti SC Light'; color: #323333; -webkit-text-stroke: #323333; min-height: 14.0px} p.p3 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 14.0px 'Microsoft YaHei'; color: #393939; -webkit-text-stroke: #393939} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} span.s2 {font: 14.0px 'Heiti SC Light'; font-kerning: none; color: #323333; -webkit-text-stroke: 0px #323333} </style>  </p><p class=\"\"><a href=\"http://www.madisonboom.com/2018/01/19/the-2018-new-year-tvc-of-oppo/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>oppo 发布新年大片《两个小星球》</b></a>，杨幂和张彬彬演绎了两个住在不同星球上的小男孩和小女孩陪伴和成长的故事，在腾讯视频的播放量超过 1496 万次。这支广告由意类广告（GOODZILLA）代理，定位与去年由杨洋拍摄的“小人国”新年广告如出一辙。<br></p><div class=\"com-insert-embed com-insert-embeds\">\r\n\t<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n\t\t<iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"https://v.qq.com/iframe/player.html?vid=q1423yigaxe&amp;tiny=0&amp;auto=0\" allowfullscreen=\"\"></iframe>\r\n\t</figure>\r\n\t\r\n</div><p><b><a href=\"https://www.digitaling.com/projects/25419.html\" rel=\"nofollow\">周冬雨给手游《御剑情缘》拍了支移动广告</a></b>，画风是从三次元穿越到二次元。<a href=\"https://yjqy.treedom.cn/?_wv=1&amp;amp=&amp;amp=&amp;channel=2&amp;from=singlemessage&amp;hash=51a3e69c3c978ea890abbc832ad0ac7d-MTA3NzA1&amp;isappinstalled=0&amp;tdsid=1%7C10384%7C90581%7C4615\" rel=\"nofollow\">点击这里查看 H5。</a></p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180122112305mN12KdhyQISMBPzx.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.500000\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div><h3 finallycleanhtml=\"true\" nocleanhtml=\"true\">值得一提的案例</h3><p><a href=\"https://www.cocacola.co.jp/stories/cocacolajapan-staysahead\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>可口可乐今天在日本推出世界首款桃子味可乐</b></a>，可口可乐表示从 1 月到 3 月初是日本桃子味碳酸饮品的销售旺季。新产品广告以平昌冬奥会为主题，邀请日本人气女演员绫濑遥与知名花滑选手拍摄。</p><p class=\"\">日本是可口可乐第三大市场，由于日本消费者热衷于新品，日本可口可乐每年会在日本投入 100 多种新品，其中碳酸饮料占到 25%。<br></p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180122115658Sl5KxL0QRVEuagjv.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.687500\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p class=\"\"><a href=\"https://www.digitaling.com/projects/25402.html\" style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>旺旺新年广告，用嘻哈和京剧元素吐槽逢年过节的烦心事</b></a>，说用旺旺送礼堵住三姑六婆的嘴就好了。<br></p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180122113727QNP9b7JecXrolzwu.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.561429\" data-format=\"png\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><p class=\"\">以及，<a href=\"http://socialbeta.com/t/jiafangyifang-news-20180119\" style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>三年六班的李子明又拍广告了</b></a>，这次是李子明的女朋友在神旺大酒店呼叫李子明的故事，客户为旺旺集团旗下神旺大酒店联手天猫精灵推广其智能客房服务。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180122115028Xbld5rnRogc208vJ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.563164\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p><a href=\"https://www.digitaling.com/projects/25408.html\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>继去年《一秒瞬媳养成班》，舒洁 VIVA 厨房纸巾再次推出《一秒瞬媳‧后传》</b></a><strong>，</strong>以清朝后宫的婆媳关系为情境拍摄一支新年广告，属于把广告里的婆媳关系处理得不太尬、有点逗的案例。<br></p><div class=\"com-insert-embed com-insert-embeds\">\r\n\t<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n\t\t<iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"https://v.qq.com/iframe/player.html?vid=i0534mhwcxl&amp;tiny=0&amp;auto=0\" allowfullscreen=\"\"></iframe>\r\n\t</figure>\r\n\t\r\n</div><p class=\"\"><a href=\"https://www.digitaling.com/projects/25412.html\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>麦当劳“麦麦小课堂”做了一组李雷和韩梅梅的条幅漫画</b></a>，教你过年到国外怎么点麦当劳。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180122114719oCBXj3yJaGSbprft.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"2.157812\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>其他，也挺重要</h3><p class=\"\"><a href=\"http://www.madisonboom.com/2018/01/19/the-list-of-the-hottest-kol-last-year/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>巴黎银行发布 KOL 报告</b></a>，国内时尚博主购买转化率最高的是黎贝卡，其次是 gogoboi 和包先生。根据微博粉丝数量得出的明星 KOL 排名显示，前三为 Angelababy、杨幂和范冰冰。在今年巴黎银行报告在时尚博主 KOL 榜单中，新增加了微信转化的指标。<br></p><p class=\"\"><a href=\"http://www.adweek.com/creativity/spotify-gets-into-pet-adoption-after-learning-dogs-have-their-own-musical-tastes/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>流媒体音乐平台 Spotify 和德国的宠物收容所合作，记录了这些狗都喜欢什么曲风</b></a>。根据格拉斯哥大学最近的一项研究表明，每只狗都有自己独特的音乐品味。<br></p><p class=\"\">题图来源：肯德基</p><style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 14.0px 'Heiti SC Light'; color: #323333; -webkit-text-stroke: #323333} p.p2 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 26.0px Times; color: #b31714; -webkit-text-stroke: #323333; min-height: 32.0px} p.p3 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 26.0px 'Songti SC'; color: #b31714; -webkit-text-stroke: #323333} p.p4 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 26.0px Times; color: #b31714; -webkit-text-stroke: #323333} p.p5 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 10.0px 0.0px; line-height: 23.0px; font: 14.0px 'Microsoft YaHei'; color: #393939; -webkit-text-stroke: #393939} p.p6 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 26.0px Times; color: #b31714; -webkit-text-stroke: #393939} p.p7 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 26.0px Times; color: #b31714; -webkit-text-stroke: #393939; min-height: 32.0px} p.p8 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 26.0px 'Songti SC'; color: #b31714; -webkit-text-stroke: #393939} p.p9 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 18.0px 'Microsoft YaHei'; color: #4d4f52; -webkit-text-stroke: #4d4f52} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} span.s2 {font: 26.0px Times; font-kerning: none; color: #b31714} span.s3 {font: 26.0px Times; font-kerning: none} span.s4 {font: 26.0px Times; font-kerning: none; color: #b31714; -webkit-text-stroke: 0px #393939} </style>"}